&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>The model is a CRNN (Convolutional Recurrent Neural Network) trained with CTC (Connectionist Temporal Classification) loss, allowing it to recognize sequences of characters from variable-length handwritten inputs without needing explicit alignment between input and labels.&lt;/p></description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://mcorgi.github.io/docs/installation/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>